                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to Minister
                            <persName type="to">Pearson</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-01-08">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 8, 1906</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Root approves Mr. Pearson’s refusal to initiate direct negotiations with the
                    Kurd accomplices, as reported in his telegram of the 8th.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
